.DS_Store
node_modules/
skill-forge-workspace/

# Scaffolded throwaway projects. CONTRIBUTING tells you to create these in the
# repo ROOT to self-check a pack (`init Throwaway --platform <id>`), and CI
# scaffolds Test* projects there too. Never commit one: the leakage gate scans
# tracked files and a real scaffold would also bloat the repo. Anchored with a
# leading "/" so template Tests/ dirs (e.g. packs/vapor-api/Tests) stay tracked.
/Throwaway/
/Test*/

# `npm pack` output (release-gate dry runs).
*.tgz
